        {
            "title": "美國暫緩對中國半導體徵收新關稅 以免加劇美中經貿關係緊張",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國指責中國在半導體領域從事不公平貿易行為，但決定至少在2027年年中之前，不對晶片進口加徵額外關稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國貿易代表辦公室(USTR)周二公佈了依據《貿易法》第301條對中國晶片開展調查的結果。該調查始於前總統喬·拜登政府任期的最後幾個月，並在總統唐納德·川普與中國國家主席習近平達成關稅休戰期間完成。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國貿易代表辦公室在聯邦公報發布的通知寫道，「中國瞄準半導體行業的主導地位是不合理的，對美國商業構成負擔或限制，因此可以採取行動。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5ce5cf8e-e4c8-34da-844b-b863f8458c28-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管此次未宣布立即徵收關稅，美國政府仍釋放出未來可能加徵關稅的信號。初始關稅稅率將在未來18個月內維持為零，並將於2027年6月23日上調至「將在該日期至少提前30天公佈的稅率」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國駐華盛頓大使館未立即回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">暫緩加徵新關稅的決定被視為川普政府試圖穩定中美關係、並鞏固川普與習近平10月在韓國達成協議的最新信號。根據該協議，華盛頓與北京同意避免徵收極端高額關稅，並放鬆對技術和關鍵礦產的出口限制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國貿易代表辦公室依法必須在去年12月調查啟動後的12個月內公佈301調查結果。去年，拜登在另一項301調查中下令將中國半導體的關稅稅率提高至50%。通過保留進一步上調關稅的選項，川普預留了新的潛在施壓工具，以防他與習近平的關稅協議破裂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">調查報告認定，中國「採取了日益激進且全面的非市場政策」來扶持本國半導體產業，並試圖製造外國對其產品的依賴，從而使美國商業處於不利地位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">可能面臨潛在新關稅的產品包括二極管、晶體管、原硅、電子集成電路及其他投入品。目前來看，這不適用於含有中國晶片的成品，例如電腦和智慧手機。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Holds Off on New Chinese Chip Tariffs Amid Trump-Xi Truce</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michelle Jamrisko.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8E%E9%AB%94%E5%BE%B5%E6%94%B6%E6%96%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-%E4%BB%A5%E5%85%8D%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BF%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-152942322.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-24 01:10:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國第三季度經濟成長4.3% 創出兩年來最快增速",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受消費者和企業支出強韌以及貿易政策趨於穩定等因素的推動，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國經濟;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/美國經濟\">美國經濟</a>在第三季度創出兩年來最快增速。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國經濟分析局周二發布的報告顯示，第三季度經通膨調整後的國內生產毛額折合年率成長4.3%。此前第二季度成長3.8%，同樣受到居民支出帶動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國經濟分析局原定於10月30日發布GDP的初步估計數字，但由於政府停擺，該報告被取消。該機構通常會對季度GDP發布三次估算，隨著更多數據出爐而不斷微調預測，但對於美國歷史上創紀錄政府停擺之前的這一個季度，它將只發布兩次估算。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1bcc2084-be49-39ad-aa64-88e33c14cc99-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Economy Expanded at 4.3% Pace, Fastest in Two Years</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Cecile Daurat、Julia Fanzeres、Augusta Saraiva.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%88%90%E9%95%B74-3-%E5%89%B5%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F-134230448.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-23 22:25:50",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "加拿大經濟在10月下滑後出現成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Statistics Canada\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HDOc8I5OJRiMHyWCWKWFug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/35fefd002c673d876605f300565166be\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Statistics Canada</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 儘管面臨美國關稅壓力，加拿大經濟仍展現出韌性，初步數據顯示該國經濟上月小幅成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加拿大統計局周二發布的初值數據顯示，分行業的國內生產毛額(GDP)在11月成長0.1%。而10月GDP下降0.3%，與彭博調查的經濟學家對當月萎縮的預估相符。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gNAaeQrlTannBxe2Xpr_gg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/22e1b12d9316c744aa27fee425a4eba7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">製造業板塊在10月下滑1.5%，基本抵消了前一個月的成長，主要原因是機械製造業下滑。木製品製造業錄得2020年4月以來的最大跌幅，反映出在美國政府從10月14日開始對加拿大木材加徵關稅後，相關生產活動放緩。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-29365b37-2da3-3c05-846a-544c74c81b4c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Canada Economy Grew in November Following October Dip (1)</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Mario Baker Ramirez、Laura Dhillon Kane.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%A810%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91%E5%BE%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-142501540.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-23 23:20:49",
