        {
            "title": "銅價觸及新高突破12,000美元 關稅政策攪動市場格局",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"IHS Markit\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yc87jm9UDhJ4NAjTmLHF6Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d1f2733e6853dd0cf260c1557023f294\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">IHS Markit</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 銅價觸及歷史新高，突破每噸12,000美元，因礦山嚴重停產及美國總統川普關稅政策引發的貿易紊亂，使這種關鍵工業金屬有望創下2009年以來最大年度漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">倫敦金屬交易所銅價一度上漲0.9%，至每噸12,031.50美元，延續了今年以來累計上漲約37%的漲勢。川普對銅徵收關稅的可能性一直以來是推動價格上漲的核心因素，美國全年進口量激增，迫使其他地區的製造商展開競價戰以保住供應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管中國（全球約半數銅的消費國）基本面需求急劇惡化，銅價仍持續攀升，足見關稅對全球貿易流的影響之深。投資者常將銅價視為全球工業活動的晴雨表，但中國經濟放緩並未抑制銅價漲勢。隨著交易員為規避潛在關稅而加速向美國運銅，市場普遍預期銅價將持續走高。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9120d3e7-98cc-3588-8130-a7e3730ac502-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">供應端也遭遇嚴重中斷，美洲、非洲和亞洲各地礦山停產引發警告：行業正面臨重大缺口，這將進一步助推價格上漲。德意志銀行警告稱，全球最大礦商的產量今年將下降3%，2026年可能再次下滑。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行分析師在報告中指出，「2025年是供應嚴重動盪的一年，多家大型礦山面臨重大運營挑戰」，並補充道，「總體而言，我們認為市場正處於明顯短缺狀態。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/U.71t9kA8KuTLGDzqeZpQg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/81f079098a58b26c114221ea73aba1d6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Copper Hits $12,000 for First Time as Tariff Trade Upends Market</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8A%85%E5%83%B9%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B412-000%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%94%AA%E5%8B%95%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80-110859106.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-23 19:45:41",
